After importing the plugin into your XCode project, double check your *-Info.plist file add the following K/V pair:

Supported External Accessory Protocols: [ Item 0: com.koamtac.kdc ]

![Supported External Accessory Protocols](http://i.imgur.com/dF2e2LK.png)

It should be added automatically by the plugin, but you know.... cordova.
